description				"Ewok

Class: Arc Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A small spear wielder with powerful/magical stones which have intense knockback. 

Weaponry: 
- Spear *
- Stones *

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Spear
- Based on lightsaber
- Can use Yellow, Red, and Purple styles
- Deals half damage per hit

--- Stones
- Based on frag grenades
- Secondary mode only
- Detonates on contact with surfaces
- 3 per life

Attributes:
- Assemble
- Heal (1)
- Reinforcements (2)

Abilities:
- Stamina (2) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (3) [Alt Ability 1]

Ewoks were a diminutive species of furry bipeds native to the forest moon of Endor.
They were most notable for helping the Rebel Alliance defeat the forces of the Galactic Empire at the Battle of Endor, allowing the shield generator there to be destroyed, and in turn, the DS-2 Death Star."